quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  38,62,"Ɓeya wi'i: \"Ko haɗi men yi'ugol worɓe, ɓe men limtaynoo e bomɓe ɓen"
  38,63,"Hara men jogitorno ɓe ton jalnori, kaa ko gite (amen) yawti ɓe"
  38,64,"Pellet, ka goonga, ko ɗum woni yeddondiral yimɓe Yiite ɓen"
  38,65,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko mi jertinoowo. Reweteeɗo woo alaa, si wanaa Allah Gooto, Fooluɗo On"
  38,66,"Jeyɗo kammuuli ɗin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde ɗin ɗiɗi, Fooluɗo, Haforoowo On"
  38,67,"Maaku: \"(Ndee Alqur'aanaare), ko nde kabaaru mawɗo"
  38,68,kono hiɗon ɗuurnii ɗum
  38,69,"Ganndal alanaano lam, e fii mbatu ngun dowrowu, tuma nde ɓe wennjaynoo"
  38,70,"Wahayinaaka e am, si wanaa wonnde min on, ko mi jertinoowo ɓanngina"
  38,71,"Janto nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: \"Min ko Mi tagiroowo ɓanndinke, immorde loopal"
  38,72,"si Mi fotindirii mo, Mi wuttii e makko ruuhu Am on, haray suuyanee mo sujjon"
  38,73,Malaa'ika'en fow sujji ɓe denndaangal
  38,74,"si wanaa Ibuliisa, o mawnintinii, o woni jeyaaɗo e yedduɓe ɓen"
  38,75,"(Allah) daali: \"Ko an yo Ibuliisa, ko haɗu maa sujjangol ko Mi tagiri juuɗe Am? A mawnintini kaa a jeya e townitiiɓe ɓen?\" @Corrected"
  38,76,"O wi'i: \"Ko min ɓuri mo moƴƴude. A tagirii lam e yiite, A tagirii mo kanko e loopal"
  38,77,"O daali: \"Yaltu ton, an on, ko a riiwaaɗo"
  38,78,"pellet, kuddi Am ndin fawike ma haa Ñalnde njoɓdi diina"
  38,79,"(Ibuliisa) wi'i : \"Joomi am, nennitanam, haa ñalnde nde ɓe immintintee"
  38,80,"O daali: \"A jeyaama e nennitanteeɓe ɓen"
  38,81,haa e ñalaande happu anndaaɗo
  38,82,"O wi'i: \"Mi woondirii mawngu Maa ngun ! Ma mi bewnuɓe fow maɓɓe"
  38,83,"si wanaa jeyaaɓe Maa, laɓɓinaaɓe ɓen e maɓɓe"